"nadomestni dnevi, dnevi nadomestnega počitka itd.)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1857
msgid ""
"Fixed or hourly salary, variable remuneration, bonuses, meal vouchers, eco "
